@Guts2112 Yes, definitely highlights the benefit of holding a cat. Pets can complete a max of 10 quests a day, so thereâ€™s a potential to earn 10x a combination of those $MILK rewards shown above. Still hard to compare to the passive yield cats generate.

Cool Pets are going to be an exciting new phase of @coolcatsnft and I'm grateful to be apart of it!
There's a lot more info available at https://t.co/B5R685SCTF if you're still interested. Peace out âœŒï¸

If you're too busy to complete Quests, you can stake your Pet any time from day 1 in the Adventures Guild. You can't complete Quests while Pets are staked, but you can still interact with them with items. The amount of $MILK earned via staking will be less than completing Quests.

There are different types of Quests with different rarities, ranging from Common to Legendary. Below shows the amount of $MILK that can be earned upon completion of each type of Quest. https://t.co/7MviCxL8cw

There are 2 main ways to acquire $MILK as a Cool Pet owner: Complete Quests or stake your Pet in the Adventures Guild. 

Quests are adventures your Pet can go on to earn $MILK for items. There is a limit of 10 Quests per day that your Pet can complete.

Not all items are the same... each item has it own 'mood' which will affect your Pets affinity to each of the elements. Not all items are equal either... some will have a greater effect on your Pets elemental affinities than others. Some even impact multiple elements.

Below are the number of interactions that your Pet needs to have to evolve to the next stage. There is a limit of 5 items that a Pet can interact with each day. 
Therefore, Final Form = 10 days minimum. https://t.co/Lr5IgAmxlS

There are four stages in the evolution of your Pet: 
Egg -> Hatching -> Hatched -> Final Form https://t.co/dx9TpVeCvg

Your Pet is minted as an unhatched egg, and the best part is YOU get to determine the final form of your Pet! Growing your Pet involves buying items for your Pet to play with or consume. These items are purchased from the Cool Shop with $MILK. https://t.co/2QnWLm86Pe
There are 9,999 Pets available to claim for free + gas for Cool Cats holders, and a further 10,000 available to mint for the public for 0.5 eth + gas.

Sapphire Town within Cooltopia is where the story of the CATaclysm takes place. The CATaclysm consists of 4 major disasters which represent the four elements of the Cool Pets: Fire, Water, Grass and Air. https://t.co/0dPHjyrmjZ
